## PickResult.userData property

Optional user data that has been defined in the picked object. This object points directly to information contained in the original \[\[TileFeatureData\]\] stored in \[\[MapView\]\], and should not be modified.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
userData?: any;
```
